com.iota.iri.conf

Interface IotaConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    APIConfig, Config, ConsensusConfig, DbConfig, IXIConfig, MilestoneConfig, NetworkConfig, NodeConfig, PearlDiverConfig, ProtocolConfig, SnapshotConfig, TipSelConfig, ZMQConfig
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseIotaConfig, MainnetConfig, TestnetConfig

    public interface IotaConfig
extends APIConfig, NodeConfig, IXIConfig, DbConfig, ConsensusConfig, ZMQConfig, TipSelConfig, PearlDiverConfig
    A container for all possible configuration parameters of IRI. In charge of how we parse the configuration from given inputs.
